46
00:02:58,580 --> 00:03:00,060
All locked in the safe.

47
00:03:20,460 --> 00:03:23,100
Finally found proof of their opium deal.

48
00:03:24,020 --> 00:03:26,660
The Marshal of Song City is after opium?

49
00:03:26,860 --> 00:03:28,460
Then I shall lure him in.

50
