69
00:07:21,660 --> 00:07:23,420
Boss, this is the man.

70
00:07:24,300 --> 00:07:26,100
Why did you return without telling me?

71
00:07:27,060 --> 00:07:28,460
Sorry, sir.

72
00:07:29,500 --> 00:07:31,420
Something important was stolen.

73
00:07:32,300 --> 00:07:33,740
To catch the thief,

74
00:07:34,180 --> 00:07:35,100
please

75
00:07:35,340 --> 00:07:36,420
work with us.

76
00:07:37,860 --> 00:07:40,380
Shut up! Do you know who he is?

77
00:07:40,700 --> 00:07:43,340
He is the son
of Song City Military Governor.

78
00:07:43,340 --> 00:07:44,980
Chen Wenbin, Marshal Chen!

79
00:07:46,200 --> 00:07:47,320
[Invitation]

80
00:07:50,180 --> 00:07:52,460
And he is my fiancé.

81
00:07:53,020 --> 00:07:54,380
I was blind.

82
00:07:54,820 --> 00:07:55,420
My apologies,

83
00:07:55,940 --> 00:07:57,020
Marshal Chen,

84
00:07:57,620 --> 00:07:58,540
Miss Wang.

85
00:08:03,080 --> 00:08:08,320
[Memory of
Lin Qingyi, Lin Wenruo, and Lin Zongyao]

86
00:08:17,060 --> 00:08:18,460
Do you want to know

87
00:08:18,900 --> 00:08:21,260
